{"tid":1766862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲有人推三罷？","createTime":"2019-12-03T01:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T04:02:37.000Z","uid":87122,"like":8,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"099d241661ac36a8f23052080ec99b11416d92bb","tid":1766862,"uid":87122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"大部份人都唔罷，香港最重要嘅股巿、機場等都無停，做唔到三罷嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n罷工要主動先叫罷工，而家示威變示弱，罷工變阻路。<br />\n<br />\n三罷嘅目的係唔返工唔返學去集會示威乜乜乜，但無人罷，罷嘅變成唔知做乜。<br />\n<br />\n推唔郁就應該搞其他嘢，呢啲先叫 be water。<br />\n<br />\n 不割蓆、不篤灰、不分化，有無人答到我點解？"},{"pid":"898d9727abc3b1064e4625e2010d809452ecb7e5","tid":1766862,"uid":87122,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"答唔到齋比負評，做乜 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce077936030e47921fe3232a0547a40cee016964","tid":1766862,"uid":87122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"808afcfa59feb15970faa95dcabd37788e22a805","tid":1766862,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab91ade9264ab5672480f1d53ce140dbd3e19297","tid":1766862,"uid":87122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:47:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3aa1f93f5879cbc52245a81af2423f56b7bd0237","tid":1766862,"uid":258646,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"我其實唔介意啊，合法遲到，食埋個靚早餐返10:30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de836ae1ad74e4f1d2300baf8a05297a6a607512","tid":1766862,"uid":258646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:55:33.000Z","msg":"最緊要新聞有報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c258669be725f335e09cadeb8de8919